abstract: Tiger Woods plays professional golf for first time in 466 days at Hero World Challenge at Albany Golf Club in Nassau, the Bahamas, and there are flashes of his old mastery during course of his play.

headline.print_headline: Flashes of Old Swagger in a Humbling Return
headline.main: Tiger Woods Shows Some Magic, Then Shows Some Rust

snippet: In his first competitive round in over a year, Woods birdied four of his first eight holes, then had two double-bogeys and a bogey after the turn to finish one over par....
lead_paragraph: In his first competitive round in over a year, Woods birdied four of his first eight holes, then had two double-bogeys and a bogey after the turn to finish one over par.
